113
00:08:21,910 --> 00:08:24,420
Is our money frozen then?

114
00:08:25,340 --> 00:08:28,860
What about getting a loan? We can pay more points.

115
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:35,010
The banks, brokerages, investment funds... I've sought all of them out.

116
