531
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:10,010
it seems that every one of them wasn't a good match for me, according to you. Right?

532
00:40:10,010 --> 00:40:12,140
What's the matter with you now?

533
00:40:13,430 --> 00:40:14,910
Old Lin,

534
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:18,650
