538
00:40:30,350 --> 00:40:32,130
You know it.

539
00:40:32,740 --> 00:40:36,560
When I take this step, there's no going back.

540
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,920
Answer me.

541
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:43,150
Do you want me to propose to Chu Ting?

542
00:40:53,460 --> 00:40:55,420
I can only say,

543
00:40:57,610 --> 00:41:01,110
